title: The Mystery of the Ocean Star - A Collection of Maritime Sketches
creator: W. Clark Russell
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of The Mystery of the Ocean Star - A Collection of Maritime Sketches, by W. Clark Russell. This is a collection of short stories of mystery and romance, set at sea, in the times of the great sea voyages. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B Part 1 (133MB) Download M4B Part 2 (141MB)
